通过12345市民服务热线答复多位市民，表示目前区级商务委与市场监管部门、公安机关正考虑联合打击。市民发现有类似违法犯罪的行为可以第一时间报警，避免违法行为扩大化。 详情请见：https://www.shobserver.com/staticsg/res/html/web/newsDetail.html?id=825388&v=1.4&sid=67"},"attached_info":"CkEIwsKJorCHqqB9EAMaCTExMjI5MjYxNCDTouW6BjAAOLMIQA5yCjY1ODAwNDY4NjZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"27 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-57b0556f8e7351634b86c1122ec2dab5_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"15_1734459882.432931","card_id":"Q_531730403","target":{"id":531730403,"title":"《花束般的恋爱》男女主维持五年的恋爱最终凋谢，到底是什么使男女主感情破灭？又有什么解决方法呢?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/531730403","type":"question","created":1651899946,"answer_count":38,"follower_count":180,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[68,740,36651,115410,732157],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"我感觉，恋爱都是这样的，在最初的新鲜感过后，取而代之的是婚姻的平淡，换言之，平淡是必然的，然而我感觉女主却不太这么想，女主貌似接受不了这种平淡。女主又交了一个npy，但是到最后，两人的感情不还是要归于平淡吗？"},"attached_info":"Cj8IwsKJorCHqqB9EAMaCDgwNDQ0NDAxIKr815MGMAA4tAFAD3IJNTMxNzMwNDAzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"26 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-9cbfd2e5c6a6a1446643e1efec581edc_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"16_1734459882.433244","card_id":"Q_651450814","target":{"id":651450814,"title":"如果《甄嬛传》华妃穿了纯元旧衣，皇上会怎么办?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/651450814","type":"question","created":1712113752,"answer_count":56,"follower_count":97,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2102,9175,76577,227955,362315],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IwsKJorCHq